I've updated 2015-10-09-netbsd-hpcarm.img.gz for hpcarm.

ftp://ftp.jp.netbsd.org/pub/NetBSD-jp/misc/jun/hpcarm/2015-10-09-netbsd-hpcarm.img.gz

http://movapic.com/pic/2015012400560454c2eda44b7d3

Feature:
- NetBSD 7.99.21-201510052020ZZ hpcarm from nyftp.netbsd
- pkgsrc-current 2015Q3 tarball from ftp.NetBSD.
- dmesg:
  https://github.com/ebijun/NetBSD/blob/master/dmesg/earm/WS011SH

Pre-compiled packages:
- Pre-compiled packages path setting: see /etc/pkg_install.conf 
PKG_PATH=ftp://ftp.jp.netbsd.org/pub/NetBSD-jp/misc/jun/NetBSD7/2015Q3/earm/
 To install application.
 # pkg_add some_application_name

 If you update pkgsrc by yourself,comment out /etc/pkg_install.conf and check
 /etc/mk.conf.

Todo:
- NetBSD7 crushed during boot: need some pullup.
- wscons=YES : boot hangs.

=====================


- NetBSD 7.99.21 base
- Copy image to Mini/MicroSD.
- Set WZERO3.
- boot hpcboot.exe
-- select Machine
-- select root partition
  and comes as you are as you want to be.
- login root (no passwd)
- check symblic link:
  default:
  ls -l /etc/X11/xorg.conf -> xorg.conf.ws011sh
- startx

  # startx

Features:
  - fit size for 2GB SD Card
  - with X11
  - pkgsrc: 2015Q3 tree inside.
  - pre-build packages
    ftp://ftp.netbsd.org/pub/NetBSD/misc/jun/hpcarm/earm/2015-02-07/

Installed Packages:
 none


Keyboard layout checkpoint:
/etc/wscons.conf
 #encoding sv
 #encoding us.swapctrlcaps
 encoding jp

/root/.xinitrc
 setxkbmap -model jp106 jp

Build sample script:
 https://github.com/ebijun/NetBSD/tree/master/hpcarm/Image

Guide:
 https://github.com/ebijun/NetBSD/blob/master/Guide/WZERO3.rst

